title: Seven volume 1 issue 1 to 7
description:
Seven is a comic series made by seven artists and seven writers consisting of seven issues about seven different people.

For the rest of the plot you have to read the comics :P

------------------------------------------------------------
PS: If you want to request a comic, please make a post here: https://forum.suprbay.org/forumdisplay.php?fid=51
and add as title something like [scanlation] title_of_comic.
It makes it easier for me to keep track of requests :P

------------------------------------------------------------
Note:

If you never read E-comics before, you should download a program like ComicRack, (you can find that here: http://www.softpedia.com/get/Multimedia/Graphic/Graphic-Viewers/ComicRack.shtml).
Then, you can use ".cbr files and open them with ComicRack.
It's easy to use, and has a great quality!

Hope you enjoy!
